::Kaiser::
       He lands with a more graceful thud away from the gunfire and 
approaches the gathering with his arms spread to signify his peaceful 
intentions.  He shakes his head and laughs at the Predacon.  "He was calling 
one of you a spy not one of these two.  They just arrived thus not spies.  
Now then if we can move past this point like the intelligent bots that we 
are."  He turns back to Prometheus.  "I am Kaiser, second in command of the 
Tripredacus faction."  He half grins.  "Welcome to Earth."

--part1_146.a021f1a.2b771745_boundary
